paragraphs.text:
{
val column = z.angular("column").toString
val numBins = z.textbox("막대 개수", "10").toString
val group = z.select("그룹", categoricalColumns(0), categoricalColumns.map(x => (x, x))).toString

z.angularBind("numBins", numBins)
z.angularBind("group", group)

z.run("20180525-210931_1055336996")
}

%sql
WITH
target (
SELECT
    ${column} AS x,
    ${group} AS grp
FROM ${table}
WHERE ${column} IS NOT NULL  -- NULL 제거
),
stats (
SELECT
    MIN(x) AS x_min,
    ${numBins} AS num_bins,
    (MAX(x) - MIN(x)) / ${numBins} AS bin_width  -- bin 너비 계산
FROM target
),
bin_tmp (
SELECT
    x, grp,
    FLOOR((x - x_min) / bin_width) AS bin  -- 각 값이 어느 bin에 속하는지 계산
FROM
    target
    CROSS JOIN stats
),
bin (
SELECT
    x, grp, 
    CASE WHEN bin = num_bins THEN num_bins - 1 ELSE bin END AS bin  -- 마지막 bin의 범위를 90 ~ 99이 아닌 90 ~ 100이 되도록
FROM
    bin_tmp
    CROSS JOIN stats
),
bin_stats (  -- 각 bin의 여러 통계량 계산 (x축에 나타낼 값들)
SELECT
    bin,
    AVG(x) AS bin_avg,
    MIN(x) AS bin_min,
    MAX(x) AS bin_max,
    MIN(bin_width) * bin AS bin_start,
    MIN(bin_width) * (bin + 1) AS bin_end
FROM
    bin
    CROSS JOIN stats
GROUP BY bin
),
bin_grp (
SELECT
    bin, grp, COUNT(*) AS bin_grp_cnt
FROM bin
GROUP BY bin, grp
)
SELECT bin, grp, bin_grp_cnt, bin_avg, bin_min, bin_max, bin_start, bin_end
FROM
    bin_grp
    JOIN bin_stats USING (bin)
ORDER BY bin, grp
